title: Trump says guns will be top of the agenda with governors
text:
Trump says guns will be top of the agenda with governors Sunday, February 25, 2018 - 01:04 
As U.S. President Donald Trump hosted governors for dinner at the White House on Sunday, he said discussions on guns will be on their agenda as they meet this week. Rough Cut
